# Data Model: astraAllVisitThePayne


Results from the ThePayne astra pipeline for each visit


## Contents
- [Basic Information](#basic-information)
- [Changelog](#changelog)
- [Example HDUS List](#example-hdus-list)
- [Notes](#notes)

---

## Basic Information
Results from the ThePayne astra pipeline for each visit. 

### Naming Convention
$MWM_ASTRA/0.5.0/summary/astraAllVisitThePayne-0.5.0.fits.gz

### Releases
IPL3

### Enviroments
MWM_ASTRA

### Approximate Size
1 GB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
astra

### Is a VAC
False

### HDUS List for release IPL3
  - [HDU0: PRIMARY](#hdu0-primary)
  - [HDU1: ](#hdu1-)
  - [HDU2: ](#hdu2-)

---

Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
